OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FCladding: Michael Gove to  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fvow to pursue firms behind 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fsafety problems            
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Housing Secretary Michael Gove is      
OL,6, vowing to "expose and pursue" firms    
OL,7, responsible for safety problems caused 
OL,8, by cladding, the BBC has learned.      
OL,10,FOn Monday, he will pledge to ease the  
OL,11,F"unfair burden" placed on leaseholders 
OL,12,Fby issues exposed by the Grenfell fire.
OL,14,FHe will set out measures aimed at      
OL,15,Fforcing developers to pay for cladding 
OL,16,Fremoval from lower-height buildings,   
OL,17,Ftelling them "we are coming for you".  
OL,19,FChanges to make it easier for owners to
OL,20,Fsell their homes will also be unveiled.
